review_title: Faded after first wash. Looks old and dinghy!!
reviews: I would of did 5 star but after the first wash they faded drastically!! They look very old and dinghy now. I'm not to happy with the outcome. I wash all my clothes by the tag. Other than that they are great for my little one and his teething days. I wont be purchasing these again not will I reccomend them.
Absolutely love these sun glasses!! He doesn't bother them when their on his face. Awesome purchase!!!

review_title: I personally wouldn't reccommend unless you like this brand company
reviews:
It seems a bit puffy for my boyfriends liking and I agree once I seen it on him. I had to send the first one back because I didn't realize that the sizing in the US are alot bigger than Canada sizing. So i had to get 2 sizes smaller than what I had actually got. So instead of an xl I ended up getting my boyfriend a medium and it still looked big on him.
I won't be buying carhartt in the future ever again.
I personally wouldn't reccommend unless you like this brand company.
Fits my head and also my boyfriends head.

review_title: Great quality. I loved it but my son had ...
reviews: My son is 3 and a half months. 1 week from 4 months old. I completely forgot this in the back of my closet!! I first tired it on him around 2 weeks old and it was so huge on him and I had put it away. I wish I could have used it while I got the chance. I will either regift it or save it for my next child! Great quality. I loved it but my son had no patience as it was tight to put his arms through and zip to it up. This one is 0-3months. I wouldn't reccommend getting 0-3 months because the arms are so small. But id reccommend getting a bigger size. All a baby needs in winter is a fluffy bear jumpsuit and a few blankets to cover while being taken out to appointments. Other than that they shouldn't get this in the smallest size.

review_title: Great quality. Wipes smell stronger. Great night light during late night diaper changes
reviews: I bought this before I had my son. Early November 2017. I had this plugged in ever since and it's March 16th, 2018; 4 months later. I absolutely love it! My son loves it. I wonder how much longer it will last haha. The wipes smell stronger. Just make sure to keep the cover closed otherwise the first few top wipes will dry out. I highly reccommend.

Fits like a glove. Haha
I purchased one for my boyfriend and myself fall 2017. It is now march 2018 and thought I'd give my review. We live in a very cold area when it's winter time and honestly they weren't as warm as I thought they would be. My fingertips would be cold. I used mine all winter because I wasn't really outside for long but my boyfriend who spends more time outside hunting, shoveling, etcc.. He needed to buy a whole new different brand. For warmth I do not reccommend.
Love love love these toys! More than I expected. And I love that the big bottle turns into a piggy bank. My son is pleased with them.

review_title: It is the best seat to invest in. Fast 2 day shipping
reviews: It is the best seat to invest in!! Giving 4 star because it's not true to color and when I opened it the packaging looked like it was open. I was hoping like a vibrant like color but it's a bit of a dull lime. Other than that I absolutely love it!!! It's great. My son also loves being in it!!!

reviews: I ordered too large BUT I LOVED THE QUALITY OF IT WHEN MY BF TRIED IT ON so i went and ordered 2 sizes smaller because american sizes are bigger compared to Canadian sizes! Will be buying more!!
